|WKBSyntax:  |YKBmonitor
|WKBAliases: |YKBmon

|YKOThe monitor command toggles your hit point and spell point monitoring
on and off. Monitor will show your current hit points and spell points
each time one or the other changes, whether it be through healing, 
combat, etc.

If the monitor is toggled to bar, then hp and sp will be shown as a bar
graph, proportional to your maximums.

For heroes and above, monitor also shows Wrathful Avatar charge. In bar
mode, the avatar bar fills while charging and drains while Avatar is active.
